{"tid":774632,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個垃圾Apple app","createTime":"2018-08-10T13:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T13:04:11.000Z","uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"900bf34c04005b53c309487fd426ae61439ed72a","tid":774632,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:01:31.000Z","msg":"雖然Apple app通常比Android app好，但都有一d app亂鳩來。<br />\n幾日前我買左Cambridge Advanced Learner&rsquo;s Dictionary, 4th edition，佢老味一d普通字查唔到，例如velodrome,有d字連續出現，例例例例如coax。仲仲仲仲有好唔user friendly, 唔同意思分幾版出，查一個字要揭幾版。隻app四年前已有，更新左幾次都係咁垃圾，我想refund,send左幾封email冇人回我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nVelodrome查唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/205646_896828f0244d5cb934e3e26ff840a0ac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F205646_896828f0244d5cb934e3e26ff840a0ac.png&h=66bf538a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一頁coax<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/205751_74e372d2eb59f183991437e9293ac58c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F205751_74e372d2eb59f183991437e9293ac58c.png&h=bbba87f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下一個字又係coax,同上一頁完全相同<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/205838_7f3822afe6850cabc94f855515ddb2c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F205838_7f3822afe6850cabc94f855515ddb2c7.png&h=d424cba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第三頁，你老味係，又係coax<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/205925_9a0149651ae99410f8226474c761308d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F205925_9a0149651ae99410f8226474c761308d.png&h=39566bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第四頁先正常返<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/210034_eac64684536fbfec5c5e3ae17b0c5f82.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F210034_eac64684536fbfec5c5e3ae17b0c5f82.png&h=cad3086d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"632ba8ae4a2564a96ac5ccd98143afbd6666e251","tid":774632,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:03:30.000Z","msg":"有冇人有Oxford dictionary?同我交換ok?"},{"pid":"00d49fce787af52a1525d0c807608989c9e8bf00","tid":774632,"uid":52594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/210408_978c4284dd1685f1d131a31c702d7cf0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F210408_978c4284dd1685f1d131a31c702d7cf0.png&h=5e7a02ce&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}